  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is focused to prove that the efficacy of a 1% Bifonazole cream is superior to a
      placebo cream after non-surgical nail ablation with a 40% urea paste.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
